languages.text: "Играешь с добычей напоследок, как кошка с мышью? Что ж, ладно, ты еще молод{mf||а}. Только не забывай — терпение не самая сильная моя черта".

languages.text: "Playing with your prey like a cat? Fine, new blood, you are still young. Just remember that patience is not my strong suit."

languages.text: “你想像猫一样玩弄猎物吗？好吧，新来的，你还年轻。记好了，耐心可不是我的强项。”
languages.original_text: "Playing with your prey like a cat? Fine, new blood, you are still young. Just remember that patience is not my strong suit."

languages.text: « Vous jouez avec votre proie comme un chat ? Très bien ; vous n'êtes encore qu'{mf|un|une} novice, après tout. Mais rappelez-vous que la patience n'est pas mon fort. »
languages.original_text: "Playing with your prey like a cat? Fine, new blood, you are still young. Just remember that patience is not my strong suit."

languages.text: 「猫のように獲物をもてあそぶ？いいじゃないか、新米。お前はまだ若い。ただ、忍耐は俺が得意とする分野じゃないということを覚えておいてもらいたいな」
languages.original_text: "Playing with your prey like a cat? Fine, new blood, you are still young. Just remember that patience is not my strong suit."

traits.speaker: Quetza-al_Winterscale

languages.text: "Ihr spielt mit Eurer Beute wie eine Katze? Schön, neues Blut, Ihr seid noch jung. Bedenkt nur, dass Geduld nicht meine Stärke ist."
languages.original_text: "Playing with your prey like a cat? Fine, new blood, you are still young. Just remember that patience is not my strong suit."

languages.text: "Avınla kedi gibi oynayacak mısın? İyi bakalım taze kan, sen daha gençsin. Şunu unutma ki sabretmekte pek başarılı sayılmam."
